    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted 997.1 Carrera S featuring the 3.8L M97 horizontally opposed six-cylinder engine. This unit has been meticulously maintained with a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh Rear Main Seal (RMS), addressing the primary concerns for this chassis. The naturally aspirated powerplant utilizes VarioCam Plus for optimized valve timing, delivering seamless power through a 6-speed manual transaxle. Handling is governed by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), providing active damping adjustment for superior lateral stability. The vehicle sits on staggered alloys with recent N-spec rubber and features a factory-spec limited-slip differential. While the finish displays minor road-derived patina, the mechanical components\u2014including the cooling system and ignition coils\u2014are in peak operating condition, making this an ideal candidate for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 38500.0,
